LongSet

public LongSet(java.util.Collection s,
               java.lang.Class c)
Creates a set of Longs from various collections. If c==Persistent.class then each item in _s_ is added to the set as new Long(persistent.getInternalID()).

Parameters:
s - collection of zero or more Longs or zero or more Persistents.
c - type of data in _s_. Currently must be Long or Persistent.
See Also:
Long, Persistent
